Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.71,0:23:05.49,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}傷つきながら 笑う姿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:10.82,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,250)\frz-90\pos(20,180)\blur1}心の裏 涙が見えた
